QuestData.Title: Return and Report
QuestData.Description: It is done! Together we were able to bring down a dangerous adversary.$b$bNeptulon himself shall hear of your exploits here, $c. Allow me to extend you his thanks...$b$bYou should leave now. This place will not remain safe for long. Soon, the naga will seek vengeance for their priestess.
QuestData.LogDescription: You are to return to Cenarion Researcher Korrah at Ethel Rethor.
QuestData.RewardText: Please accept this reward for your heroic accomplishments, $n.$b$bYou have bought us precious time!
